13. O-O-O+ Nd7 { Black developed pretty well, but the king on d8 is still not fully comfortable. } 
14. Rg1 Be7 
15. Bg2 { Black's light-squared bishop is no worse than ours now, so we may as well trade it. } Bxg2 { The choice of all the correspondence players. } 
16. Rxg2 Kc7 {[%csl Ga8,Gc7,Gh8]} { Black is trying to solve the problem of the king. } 
