10. f4 {[%mdl 32768]} { The plans with f4-f5 are the most brutal apparently. } Nc6 
11. Rg1 {[%cal Gg1g3,Gf4f5]} { The rook is great on g3 it turns out. Also, the smart thing about it is that whenever Black does Nxd4, White will recapture with the queen without wasting a tempo on Qd2. } Rc8 { A sample line. } 
12. Rg3 Be7 
13. f5 {[%csl Re6,Gf5,Gg5]} { Black's position is just collapsing, it is even hard to continue the sample line here, without feeling the pain for our opponents. } *

