Black has a few systems now, the most popular ones being early Nxd4 capture, forcing Qxd4, before we get the bishop to e3, the quick Bg7 Qb6 setup, trying to dislodge our knight from d4 and the old mainline, where Black just develops with Bg7 O-O d6 Bd7 and lets us finish our development undisturbed as well. There is also the old line @@StartFEN@@r1bqkbnr/pp1ppp1p/2n3p1/8/2PNP3/8/PP3PPP/RNBQKB1R b KQkq c3 0 5@@EndFEN@@ 5...Nf6 6.Nc3 Bg7 7.Be3 Ng4 , but although it looks cool, it's not very good. } ) Bg7 
