12. h4 {[%mdl 32768]} { Our standard move. We need to reinforce the g5 bishop against some tricks and it is also the right way to start pushing the kingside, not yet weakening our f3 pawn with g4, which would be vulnerable after a d5 break. } d5 ( { An attempt to make something happen in the center. The more likely play with } 12...b5 { will get the usual treatment with } 13.Ne2! { , see the 11... b5 line [/variation/24987978] for these ideas. } ) 
