3. e5 ( { White can also try to transpose to the standard open Sicilian with } 3.Nc3 { , when Black can try } 3...d5 { , to stay true to their dubious intentions. That said, I feel we should exploit Black's mistake on move 2 and not give any second chances to get back into a normal opening. } ) Nd5 ( { This is Black's only reply, if } 3...Ng4 4.h3 { knight gets kicked away. } ) 
4. Nc3 Nxc3 
