8. O-O Be7 { Black has unambitious goals of just finishing the development. } 
9. c4! { More challenging than just taking the pawns and playing against the d5 isolani. } a6 { The only way to not lose material. } 
10. exd6 ( { Also possible is to go for } 10.Ba4 dxc4 11.d5 b5 { complications, but this simple solution looks good enough to me. } ) Qxd6 
11. dxc5 Qxc5 
