13. c5 { Always feels good to go forward with tempo. } Qd8 
14. Qa4 { Just taking on c6 is also a fat plus equal according to the engines. } Bd7 
15. Be2 {[%csl Rb7,Rd5]} { We will get to press on the weak d5 and b7 pawns. } O-O 
16. Rad1 Be6 
