12. f4 { Forcing the matters. Weakening the g4-square is ugly, but things are very concrete and Black has more urgent matters than our weak squares - the king is weak. } Nc4 ( { Keeping the g4-square for the other knight. If } 12...Neg4 { then } 13.e5! { works well for us. } ) 
13. e5 { Breaking through in the center. } Ng4 
