12. Ndxb5 Qb8 
13. Bf4 d6 
14. Nxd6+! Bxd6 
15. Rxd6! { Beautiful stuff, but in fact quite thematic for 7. Qf3 variation. } Qxd6 
16. Bxe5 Qc5 
